-- Centex shares jump after Pulte buy
-- 
-- Wed Apr 8, 2009 7:35am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/08/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-centex-s-idUSTRE5372HM20090408

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Centex jumped 23 percent to $9.40 in premarket trade on Wednesday after the company agreed to be acquired by Pulte Homes for $1.3 billion in stock. 

 (Reporting by  Chuck Mikolajczak ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)